*Student Grade Calculator - Multi-Platform Implementation*

A comprehensive Student Grade Calculator application
implemented in two popular programming languages: Kotlin (Native 
Android) and Dart/Flutter (Cross-platform). This project 
demonstrates the implementation of a practical educational tool 
with file handling capabilities.

*Overview*
The Student Grade Calculator is an educational application 
designed to simplify the process of calculating student grades based
on their marks. It features a user-friendly interface, manual data 
entry, and Excel file import/export capabilities. This repository
contains two complete implementations, allowing developers to 
compare and learn from both Kotlin and Dart approaches.
